graph TB
    subgraph 流量接入层
        Gateway["Nginx/Envoy HTTP/WS 网关"]
    end

    subgraph 宿主进程_Rust ["宿主进程 (Rust)"]
        Scheduler["宿主调度器"]
        WasmRuntime["Wasm 运行时 (wasmtime)"]
        Capabilities["宿主能力层"]
        JIT["固化引擎 (JIT Harness)"]

        Scheduler -->|分配/回收| WasmRuntime
        Scheduler -->|注入配置| Capabilities
        WasmRuntime -->|宿主函数调用| Capabilities
        Capabilities -->|记录轨迹| JIT
        JIT -->|热替换模块| WasmRuntime
    end

    subgraph Wasm实例池 ["预初始化 Wasm 实例池"]
        Instance1["实例 A (线性内存)"]
        Instance2["实例 B (线性内存)"]
        InstanceN["……"]
    end

    Gateway -->|请求转发表| Scheduler
    Scheduler -->|分配实例| WasmRuntime
    WasmRuntime -->|嵌入| Instance1
    WasmRuntime -->|嵌入| Instance2
    WasmRuntime -->|嵌入| InstanceN

    subgraph 持久化层
        Redis[Redis 缓存]
        ObjectStore[对象存储]
        AuditLog[审计日志]
    end

    Capabilities -->|读写| Redis
    Capabilities -->|存储| ObjectStore
    Capabilities -->|写入| AuditLog

    subgraph 外部服务
        LLM["LLM API (OpenAI/Claude)"]
        Tools["命令行工具 (cat/python3/...)"]
    end

    Capabilities -->|网络请求| LLM
    Capabilities -->|受限执行| Tools
